OL,3,CTicketless train travel: What does
OL,4,Cthis mean for passengers?
OL,6,FTicketless train travel could be the
OL,7,Fnew norm for rail passengers under a
OL,8,Fnew scheme being trialled by East
OL,9,FMidlands Railway.
OL,11,FThe company has launched a new feature
OL,12,Fon its mobile phone app, which tracks
OL,13,Fpassenger journeys using satellite
OL,14,Ftechnology.
OL,16,FIt's now live on routes between
OL,17,FLeicester, Nottingham and Derby, and
OL,18,Fallows travellers to check-in and
OL,19,Fcheck-out on rail journeys, using a
OL,20,Flocation-identifying phone app.
