OL,3,CTicketless train travel: What does
OL,4,Cthis mean for passengers?
OL,6,FIt will track journeys using Global
OL,7,FPositioning System (GPS) technology
OL,8,Fand then charge passengers the
OL,9,Fappropriate fare at the end of the day.
OL,11,FFor ticket inspections and to go
OL,12,Fthrough ticket barriers, a unique bar
OL,13,Fcode will pop up in the app to be
OL,14,Fscanned.
OL,16,FFrom the end of September, further
OL,17,Ftrials will be launched on Northern
OL,18,Fservices to Harrogate, Leeds,
OL,19,FSheffield, Doncaster and Barnsley.
OL,21,F"You can't spend more than #23 a day"
