OL,3,CTicketless train travel: What does
OL,4,Cthis mean for passengers?
OL,6,FEMR's Commercial Director Simon Pready
OL,7,Fspoke about the East Midlands rollout.
OL,9,FHe said: "We've already done some
OL,10,Finternal testing of the app.
OL,12,F"We're confident it's robust but we
OL,13,Fwant to roll it out to a larger group
OL,14,Fand really stress test it.
OL,16,F"There are daily caps on there and you
OL,17,Fcan't spend more than #23 a day
OL,18,Ftravelling within the area if you're
OL,19,Fusing the app, so there will not be
OL,20,Fenormous charges being applied to
OL,21,Fpeople's accounts."
